{"type":"article","id":20899,"title":"洁洁良第二？疑似中科院大学学生因推特发表「不当言论」被校方关切","uid":3685,"topics":[934,375],"contents":"中国科学院大学微博发布“情况通报”，针对网传国科大学生在国外社交平台Twitter发表不当言论一事，调查组初步查明，相关言论为本校2019级硕士生季某某在国外发表，该生已经删除了在境外社交平台上发表的相关言论并公开道歉，目前正在做进一步调查，并将根据调查结果，依据校规校纪做出严肃处理。<br>\n<br>\n中科院大学发表声明将「彻查」<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ebg_uROVAAAT38J?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ebg_uROVAAAT38J?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ebg_uROVAAAT38J?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n上微博热搜了，鉴于微博刚刚被网信办约谈整肃过，可以基本肯定这此事件不是简单地粉蛆自发行为那么简单。这波大概率是墙内宣传系统有组织、有计划地杀鸡儆猴，给反贼下马威。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbhQNnlUcAARTQM?format=jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbhQNnlUcAARTQM?format=jpg\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbhQNnlUcAARTQM?format=jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n墙内粉红圈流传该人言论<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbhkumLU0AA9To-?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbhkumLU0AA9To-?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbhkumLU0AA9To-?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n疑似收到校方压力，该人已经发表「道歉声明」<br>\n（涉及真实姓名，故只放链接）<br>\n<br>\nhttps://twitter.com/opengl106/status/1276813853364498432","date":"2020-06-27","agreeCount":7,"discussionCount":0}